  "description": "Per-POS export column dictionary. This is the single most defensible asset in OpticAI: the encoded knowledge of exactly how Toast, Square, and Clover name and structure their exports, including the gotchas. A weekend clone has none of this and will mis-map columns the moment a real export is uploaded. Expand this with every new export you see in the wild \u2014 it compounds.",
