        "Quantity Sold": "quantity_sold",
        "Price": "item_revenue",
        "Modifier Name": "modifier",
        "Modifier Value": "modifier_revenue"
      },
      "gotchas": [
        "Clover often exports at the ORDER or LINE-ITEM grain, not pre-aggregated by day \u2014 expect to roll up to business date yourself.",
        "Clover timestamps are full datetimes; truncate to business date and apply the business_day_close_hour rule for late-night.",
        "Clover 'Revenue' vs 'Net Revenue' distinction is inconsistent across merchant configs \u2014 verify which is post-discount.",
        "Clover has weak native labor reporting; labor usually comes from a third-party integration with its own schema.",
        "A column labeled 'COGS' is usually TOTAL COGS (food+beverage+paper), not Food Cost alone \u2014 map to total_cogs and confirm before using as food cost.",
        "Voids (rung-but-not-made) are tracked separately from Comps/Discounts (made-and-given). Map 'Void Amount' to voids, not comps.",
        "Clover is LEDGER-grain: join Order/Line-Item/Employee logs on Order ID, filter Order Status to Paid (net out Refunded), and roll up to location-week before KPIs."
      ]
    },
